{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"49f3bb1f3c","title":"对西藏工委关于喝厦提出裁减藏军问题的处理意见的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8b0e6f5d43","index":0,"year":1954,"month":7,"day":6,"articleId":"49f3bb1f3c"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"96bfc24d0d","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"49f3bb1f3c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"喝厦，即西藏地方政府。"},{"id":"d32bd6b63e","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"49f3bb1f3c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央办公厅主任。"},{"id":"e260095026","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"49f3bb1f3c","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共西藏工委1954年7月5日给中央并军委的电报中说，喀厦今天提出，拟将现有藏军除保留警卫代本1500人外，其余全部解散还乡，态度十分急迫，想在达赖离藏前解决。我们估计他们所以提出此项意见，主要是由于财政困难所致。我们意见当达赖离开西藏的时候，突然裁减藏军，殊非时宜，拟向喝厦进行说服，争取在达赖离藏期间，不裁减藏军，一切维持现状。如他们提出财政困难，则以中央名义给以一部分补助，其他问题仍由喝厦负责。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2d33ebe729","type":"title","text":"对西藏工委关于喝厦提出裁减藏军问题的处理意见的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"49f3bb1f3c"},{"id":"96bfc24d0d","type":"paragraph","text":"尚昆同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"49f3bb1f3c"},{"id":"d32bd6b63e","type":"paragraph","text":"这类问题应由统战部拟处，是属于政治性质的，军委不好处理。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"49f3bb1f3c"},{"id":"e260095026","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"49f3bb1f3c"},{"id":"8365aa0d1c","type":"paragraph","text":"七月六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"49f3bb1f3c"}],"page":{"id":"5ba01f87cf","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"49f3bb1f3c","start":154,"end":154}}}},"__N_SSG":true}